OL,3,CReynolds gives instructions to British
OL,4,CSteel after MPs back emergency law
OL,6,FThe Business Secretary has issued
OL,7,Finstructions to British Steel, using
OL,8,Fthe emergency powers approved by
OL,9,FParliament on Saturday to save the
OL,10,FScunthorpe blast furnaces.
OL,12,FA Government source confirmed that
OL,13,FJonathan Reynolds had given directions
OL,14,Fto the company following the
OL,15,Fextraordinary sitting of Parliament.
OL,17,FBut they declined to give details of
OL,18,Fthose instructions, saying they would
OL,19,Fnot provide a running commentary on
OL,20,Fthem.
