OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,7,Fthe Government had "stepped in to save
OL,8,FBritish Steel", adding: "We are acting
OL,9,Fto protect the jobs of thousands of
OL,10,Fworkers, and all options are on the
OL,11,Ftable to secure the future of the
OL,12,Findustry."
