OL,6,FAlthough ministers still hope to
OL,7,Fsecure private sector investment to
OL,8,Fsave the plant, there are currently no
OL,9,Fcompanies offering to take it on and
OL,10,FMr Reynolds conceded to MPs that
OL,11,Fpublic ownership was "the likely
OL,12,Foption".
OL,14,FMr Reynolds said the emergency
OL,15,Flegislation was a "proportionate and
OL,16,Fnecessary step", adding he wanted it
OL,17,Fto be a "temporary position" with the
OL,18,Fpowers not lasting "any minute longer
OL,19,Fthan is necessary".
