OL,6,FThe Government has been in negotiation
OL,7,Fwith Jingye on the future of the
OL,8,FScunthorpe plant since it came to
OL,9,Fpower last year, taking on the long-
OL,10,Frunning talks between the company and
OL,11,Fthe previous government.
OL,13,FBut, opening the debate in Parliament
OL,14,Fon Saturday, Mr Reynolds said
OL,15,Fministers had decided to act after
OL,16,FJingye had failed to act "in good
OL,17,Ffaith" by deciding to stop buying raw
OL,18,Fmaterials for the blast furnaces.
