OL,6,FHe said the company had also rejected
OL,7,Fan offer from the Government to
OL,8,Fpurchase raw materials without causing
OL,9,Fany loss to Jingye, instead demanding
OL,10,Fa "frankly excessive" amount of money
OL,11,Fwith few guarantees the plant would
OL,12,Fremain open.
OL,14,FHe told MPs: "We could not, will not
OL,15,Fand never will stand idly by while
OL,16,Fheat seeps from the UK's remaining
OL,17,Fblast furnaces without any planning,
OL,18,Fany due process or any respect for the
OL,19,Fconsequences."
