OL,6,FHowever, she was unable to provide
OL,7,Fdetails of the deal, saying
OL,8,Fnegotiations were still ongoing when
OL,9,Flast year's election was called, but
OL,10,Fadding it "would have succeeded
OL,11,Fbetter" than Mr Reynolds's plan.
OL,13,FWriting in The Sunday Times, Mr
OL,14,FReynolds said the Government "refused
OL,15,Fto be extorted by a company that
OL,16,Frepeatedly refused to act rationally".
OL,18,F"The seeds of this decision were sown
OL,19,Flong before the United States opted to
OL,20,Fimpose tariffs on steel," he said.
