OL,6,F"Previous governments have been too
OL,7,Fwilling to stand idly by while heat
OL,8,Fseeped out of blast furnaces, but to
OL,9,Flose this capability now, in this
OL,10,Fmanner, would have weakened our
OL,11,Findustrial base irrevocably. Inaction
OL,12,Fwas never an option."
OL,14,FBusinesses and trade unions welcomed
OL,15,Fthe Government's decision to take
OL,16,Fcontrol of the Scunthorpe plant.
